Here an example of how the .env should look like :

```
# ========================================
# MYSQL INFOS
# ========================================
MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=your_root_password
MYSQL_DATABASE=transcendence
MYSQL_USER=your_mysql_user
MYSQL_PASSWORD=your_mysql_password

# ========================================
# LOGIN AND DOMAIN
# ========================================
LOGIN=your_login

# ========================================
# Application Configuration
# ========================================
NODE_ENV=development
NODE_VERSION=24-alpine

# ========================================
# Port Configuration
# ========================================
APP_PORT=3000
NGINX_PORT=4443
NGINX_HTTP_PORT=8080

# ========================================
# Authentification et JWT
# ========================================
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=24h
BCRYPT_SALT_ROUNDS=10

# ========================================
# Google OAuth
# ========================================
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id
GOOGLE_SECRET_ID=your_google_secret
GOOGLE_AUTH_REDIRECT=https://localhost:4443/api/auth/google/redirect

# ========================================
# 42 OAuth
# ========================================
FT_CLIENT_ID=your_42_client_id
FT_SECRET_ID=your_42_secret
FT_AUTH_REDIRECT=https://localhost:4443/api/auth/intra42/redirect
```
